<section
    style="min-height:60vh;display:flex;flex-direction:column;align-items:center;justify-content:center;padding:2rem;background:#f8f9fb;">
    <div
        style="max-width:760px;width:100%;text-align:center;box-shadow:0 12px 30px rgba(0,0,0,0.08);padding:1rem;background:#fff;">

        <h1 style="font-size:6rem;margin:0;color:#e74c3c;letter-spacing:2px;">500</h1>

        <h2 style="font-size:1.5rem;margin:0.5rem 0;color:#333;">Erro Interno do Servidor</h2>
        <p style="color:#666;margin:1rem 0 1.5rem;">
            Ocorreu um erro inesperado no servidor. Se o problema persistir, entre em contato com o suporte.
        </p>

        <div style="display:flex;flex-direction:column;align-items:center;margin-bottom:2rem;">
            <strong style="color:#333;margin-bottom:0.25rem;">Mensagem:</strong>
            <div style="background:#f8f8f8;padding:0.75rem;width:85%;border-radius:6px;color:#c0392b;overflow-wrap:break-word;">
                {{message}}
            </div>
        </div>

        {{#if stack}}
        <div style="margin-bottom:1rem;">
            <strong style="display:block;color:#333;margin-bottom:0.25rem;">Stack (detalhes para debug):</strong>
            <pre
                style="white-space:pre-wrap;background:#1e1e1e;color:#e6e6e6;padding:1rem;border-radius:6px;max-height:220px;overflow:auto;font-size:0.85rem;">{{stack}}</pre>
        </div>
        {{/if}}

        <a href="/"
            style="display:inline-block;padding:0.65rem 1rem;background:#2b2a2a;color:#fff;border-radius:6px;text-decoration:none;font-weight:600;box-shadow:0 6px 18px rgba(25, 43, 66, 0.18);">
            Voltar para a página inicial
        </a>
    </div>
</section>